{"type": "article", "id": 52424, "title": "这款空气净化器，还可以拿来养植物｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-04-22T22:59:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 49558, "name": "Zegen"}, {"id": 242, "name": "YOY"}, {"id": 49559, "name": "Dedon"}, {"id": 49560, "name": "Kettal"}, {"id": 23566, "name": "Mutina"}, {"id": 49561, "name": "Clairy"}, {"id": 31539, "name": "Pavel Vetrov"}, {"id": 16444, "name": "Barber & Osgerby"}, {"id": 22532, "name": "Patricia Urquiola"}, {"id": 49562, "name": "Hella Jongerious"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 122, "image": "img/article/article_show/201804222205030rTWnBJjpx3b8PHV.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; background-color: #ffffff} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>NATEDE Air Purifier by Clairy</h3><p>众筹网站 Kickstarter 发布了一款名为 NATEDE 的空气净化器，是旧金山创业公司 Clairy 推出的新品。</p><p>Clairy 团队认为，人们每天大约 90% 的时间都在室内，但是相比于室外，这里的空气污染程度要严重 5 倍。 NATEDE 是一款适合家庭、办公室的智能自然空气净化器。它将空气净化器和植物支架结合在一起，可以让空气通过根部，其内置的新型光催化过滤器无需更换即可消除 93％ 的 VOC，99％的细菌、病毒、微颗粒和气味。该设备装有先进的传感器，并与专用应用程序配对，可实时监测空气污染物，还可以测量房间的温度和湿度。</p><p>与普通的花盆不同，NATEDE 还具有自动浇水系统，可保持植物处于湿润中大约一个月的时间。众筹价 139 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/628579643/natede-the-most-amazing-smart-natural-air-purifier\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422220655axNtXr2y5Olf0mUd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422220655GjYmUWEo8l3RQsbN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422220655mTFhl4wdtrJqMBEV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422220655IHVDzLTetE5aYSWN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422220655lkUWr7hN3mdM9Zjx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.594444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422220655svxXOK5Mt9YDcLwG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422220655pmk9NaiV5qMr43eR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422220656gjmQnvzFqH3N5LPY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Diarama Ceramic Collection by Hella Jongerious for Mutina</h3><p>荷兰设计师 Hella Jongerious 为意大利陶瓷品牌 Mutina 设计了全新瓷砖 Diarama 系列，尝试深入研究色彩、材质与纹理。整个系列包含应用于 7 种不同的亚光彩色粘土基底上的多种彩釉色调。</p><p>“我一直将瓷砖看作是画布，我想知道如果使用不同颜色的粘土并在顶层施釉之后会发生什么。”  Hella Jongerious 表示，“这种制作方式，使得瓷砖的整体表面产生类似油画中的混合感。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422220932bnNgEf4Stiy8uXsq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669512\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422220934xFMYfj2zAHI1btpE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665446\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804222209356nyOR4CIdBJsDYTG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.673171\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422220935mpwRBhlWd4Gg13IA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.360859\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422220936TeZ8hFgY4yLRADr3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.697674\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/hella-jongerious-diarama-ceramic-collection-mutina-study-color-04-20-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Vimini Collection by Patricia Urquiola for Kettal </h3><p>西班牙鬼才设计师 Patricia Urquiola 为意大利高端户外家具品牌 Kettal 设计了 Vimini 系列，是对丹麦设计师 Nanna Ditzel 设计的 Basket 系列沙发椅的更新版本。</p><p>如果说原作称得上是现代主义风格的代表作，那 Patricia Urquiola 的更新版本则削弱了很多沙发椅的现代主义气质，将柳条与粗糙的木质框架相结合。</p><p>整个系列包括一个扶手椅、沙发和边桌，传统的编织样式为户外空间提供了一个轻松而迷人的选择。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221442P2pWgS4uCaBqNX3h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705833\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221445zy5nVs1oul0Qb8aW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221446sfJwqcjVoBOP601Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.362000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804222211315KsPu3GeivCTZdM2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.635697\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221133sNJG34LCWqBdQvTK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.613219\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221134vlq8XCNIp4VamAUB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694377\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221134TyWLRN46UhMKJ2oO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700855\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221135Fjz0kSityITCPnZh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.674020\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/patricia-urquiola-traditional-techniques-modernist-forms-kettal-04-22-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>BREA Modular Lounge System by Barber &amp; Osgerby for Dedon</h3><p>德国户外家具品牌 Dedon 推出模块化室外休闲沙发 BREA，操刀设计的是英国双人设计组合 Barber &amp; Osgerby。BREA 系列的软垫部分看起来像是与框架一体的，但其实可以随时被移除，且使用的材料不仅适用于室内而且也适用于室外。</p><p>对于 Edward Barber 和 Jay Osgerby 来说，BREA 的概念源于他们的一个想法，户外家具也应该和室内家具的设计一样注重细节上的表现力。BREA 用到了创新的管状框架结构，看起来简洁、优质且舒适，适用于单人座、双人座和三人座模块。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221604WMU2dJmBIpnsraRY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.350683\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221608CRAUWMY3uzbm7naI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.622850\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221612dZmBMGcXHqIeofgk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664216\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221612Wayp3zGEhwgn8sX1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.797419\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221616i8e7mVbWShoRAcPJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663814\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>PAINT by YOY</h3><p>我们上周分享过一款日本创意工作室 YOY 设计的时钟，与这款新品一同亮相的，还有一系列好似用涂料绘制而成的灯。</p><p>打开开关时，画布框被一个笔画点亮。灯具配备着 LED 灯和透明片，掩盖了画笔笔触的细节。将不完美的笔触精准地复制到画布上。它看上去更像是个墙面装饰品，是个会给人惊喜感的作品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221657G6lAnxy8Uu35fhLd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804222216575NUqDtiM8d6mzWgE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221657kjmlbKZCDPF1guiv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221658XV2y0l3cDRPjgmkB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221658DxJrIH9Ph6kWcKgn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221658gtEFX5TObqfUNsey.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>OLLLY Desk by Pavel Vetrov for Zegen</h3><p>OLLLY 办公桌是一款红点奖获奖作品，是乌克兰设计师 Pavel Vetrov 为其本土品牌 Zegen 设计的。很多人都喜欢把自己的办公桌收拾得干净整洁，但一旦工作起来，很难保证桌面的秩序感。</p><p>OLLLY 试图帮助用户解决这一问题，这款桌子配备了一个小巧紧凑的抽屉，用于存放一些使用率较高的小物件。另有可以放置文具的凹槽，以及用于手机和平板电脑的内置支架，有助于保持工作区域的整洁度。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221748vgfJ3HaKpBhQ5UOr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221749YXwE3gajeUsvLx8Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221749wKR16WlCGet52xSQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221750Vr86nLA7Cz5kNc3m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221750GaHQPof6cDrYtCvS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221751j0F5XuPqTQCmrONZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180422221751mOhKqJlL5zBcNfVM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498438\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.pavelvetrov.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pavel Vetrov</a></p></figcaption></figure></div>"}